## ğŸ¤“ Why so small?

- Minimal word lists (units/teens/tens)
- Irregular stems via string rewrites
(thirâ†’three, fifâ†’five, eighâ†’eight, twenâ†’two, forâ†’four, twelâ†’twelve)
- Big scales via 1000**(i+1) (not hardcoded)

